+  /**
+   * Count k-mers using dense array (for k <= 10).
+   *
+   * Returns a DenseKmerResult with counts for all 4^k possible k-mers.
+   * K-mers containing N are skipped.
+   *
+   * # Arguments
+   * * `k` - K-mer size (1-10)
+   *
+   * # Returns
+   * DenseKmerResult with counts, or empty result if k is invalid.
+   */
